{"arkId":"cl010491663","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010491663","modified ":"2025-12-10","title":"Hamlet, sa m\u00e8re et le roi","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Hamlet, sa m\u00e8re et le roi"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1834 - 1843","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1834,"endYear":1843,"imprecision":"","text":"1e moiti\u00e9 du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Delacroix, Eug\u00e8ne","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1863","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1798","place":"Charenton-Saint-Maurice (Val-de-Marne)","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q33477"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MD 2021-13","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"RF 32 252","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"AD8","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"Mus\u00e9e national Eug\u00e8ne-Delacroix","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La sc\u00e8ne repr\u00e9sente Hamlet, sa m\u00e8re et le roi, dans l\u0027acte I, sc\u00e8ne 2 d\u0027Hamlet de Shakespeare. Projet invers\u00e9, et avec variantes, en vue de la lithographie faisant partie d\u0027une s\u00e9rie de 16 auxquelles Delacroix travailla de 1834 \u00e0 1843, dont les pierres sont aujourd\u0027hui conserv\u00e9es au Mus\u00e9e Delacroix.\r\n\r\nAu centre, Hamlet esquiss\u00e9 se penche vers sa m\u00e8re, debout \u00e0 sa droite. A sa  gauche, le roi tend une main vers lui ou vers la reine (?). Sur la gauche, on retrouve la figure d\u0027Hamlet  plus aboutie. Derri\u00e8re ces trois personnages, une foule indistincte. A droite, 2 personnages